Executes ACTION-IF-EXECINFO-H-IS-FOUND when present and the execinfo.h
header is found or ACTION-IF-EXECINFO-H-IS-NOT-FOUND in case the header
seems unavailable.

Also adds -lexecinfo to LIBS on BSD if needed.

